        "heading": "Installation Guide",
        "text": "<h2>Installation Guide</h2><p>[wistia_video]</p><p>To install your new Shower Filter, you'll need the following:</p><ul><li>Qure Shower Filter</li><li>(Optional) Plumber's tape for extra leak protection (provided)</li><li>(Optional) A towel or cloth for better grip when unscrewing the showerhead</li></ul>"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_kMxw9W": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Claims & User Study",
        "text": "<h2>Product Claims & User Study</h2><p>Key claims:</p><ul><li>Fewer breakouts</li><li>Happier, hydrated skin</li><li>Less redness & irritation</li><li>Shinier & buildup free hair</li><li>Less green hues on dyed hair</li></ul><p>Results from an 8-week user study:</p><ul><li>83% reported softer hair and skin</li><li>80% saw less skin irritation, including a reduction in acne, redness, and eczema</li><li>83% noticed reduced scalp dryness, irritation, or flakiness</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_Fipjki": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "blocks": {
        "quote_TYC4wj": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "style": "blue",
            "text": "<p>Remember to <strong>add a personal touch</strong> to the messaging, talk about how the filter makes your skin feel.</p><p>Examples:</p><ul><li>“This filter changed my skin.”</li><li>“Since using this filter, my hair has never looked better!”</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "quote_TYC4wj"
      ],
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": true,
        "heading": "Content Requirements",
        "text": "<h2>Content Requirements</h2><p>Messaging must include:</p><ul><li>Easy installation of the triple-filter showerhead for the purest head-to-toe hydration.</li><li>Reduces chlorine, heavy metals & contaminants that irritate the skin, for an overall more hydrated, clearer skin.</li><li>Reduces limescale buildup which can dry out skin & hair, for smoother & softer skin and tresses.</li><li>Customizable water flow settings: Rainfall, Massage and Power Spray</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
